        damage or impair its functionality or security; and c) attempt to gain
        unauthorized access to other users' accounts or to any parts of our
        system.
      </p>
    </Term>

    <Term title="4. Data Privacy">
      <p>
        We value your privacy. Our <a
          class="text-primary-light hover:underline"
          href="privacy">Privacy Policy</a
        > outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information. By
        using Trgtz, you consent to the practices described in the Privacy Policy.
      </p>
    </Term>

    <Term title="5. Intellectual Property">
      <p class="mb-4">
        All content, trademarks, logos, and intellectual property related to
        Trgtz are owned by us or our licensors. This includes, but is not
        limited to, the app design, features, and original content.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        However, Trgtz also uses third-party resources, such as Material Icons,
        Material Components, and Google Fonts, which are the property of their
        respective owners and are used under their applicable licenses. You
        agree to comply with all third-party license agreements when using
        Trgtz.
      </p>
      <p>
        You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works based on
        our content without our written permission, except as allowed by law or
        the terms of the third-party licenses.
      </p>
    </Term>

    <Term title="6. Limitation of Liability">
