        Trgtz is provided on an "as-is" and "as-available" basis. We do not
        guarantee that the app will be error-free or that it will always be
        available. We are not liable for any damages or losses resulting from
        your use of the app.
      </p>
    </Term>

    <Term title="7. Termination">
      <p>
        We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access to Trgtz at any
        time, for any reason, including but not limited to violations of these
        Terms and Conditions.
      </p>
    </Term>

    <Term title="8. Changes to the Terms">
      <p>
        We may update these Terms and Conditions from time to time. If we make
        changes, we will notify you by posting the updated terms on the app or
        through other communication methods. Your continued use of the app after
        the changes take effect constitutes your acceptance of the new terms.
      </p>
    </Term>

    <Term title="9. Governing Law">
      <p>
        These Terms and Conditions are governed by and construed in accordance
        with the laws of Uruguay. Any disputes arising from these terms will be
        resolved in the courts of Uruguay.
      </p>
